  "instructions": [
    "Bring a large pot of salted water to a boil and cook the macaroni according to the package instructions.",
    "In a large skillet, heat the coconut oil over medium-high heat and add the chopped onion.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add the sliced mushrooms and cook until they are tender and lightly browned.",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together the tomato sauce and eggs.",
    "Add the cooked macaroni to the bowl and toss to combine with the sauce.",
    "Add the cooked onion and mushroom mixture to the bowl and toss to combine.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy."
  ],
